  <entry>
    <title>二、代码审计环境搭建</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/07/24/%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%A1%E8%AE%A1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/07/24/%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%A1%E8%AE%A1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</id>
    <published>2021-07-24T13:04:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-25T01:58:24.557Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="0x00-jdk的下载与安装"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x00-jdk的下载与安装"></a> 0x00 JDK的下载与安装</h2><h3 id="0x0000-jdk的下载"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0000-jdk的下载"></a> 0x0000 JDK的下载</h3><blockquote><p>《Java代码审计：入门篇》使用Java SE Development Kit 8u191版本进行演示</p></blockquote><ul><li>下载地址：<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html">https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html</a></li><li>版本说明：版本号“8u251”里的“u”代表的意思为“update”，“8u251”代表的意思为JDK8第251次更新的版本</li><li>版本差异：不同版本的差异可能会导致PoC需要进行改动或者无法利用成功</li></ul><h3 id="0x0001-jdk的安装"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0001-jdk的安装"></a> 0x0001 JDK的安装</h3><ul><li>Windows安装<ul><li>双击运行安装JDK</li><li>设置系统环境变量<ul><li>新建环境变量 “<strong>JAVA_HOME</strong>”，值为 “<strong>安装的JDK的路径地址</strong>”</li><li>新建环境变量 “<strong>CLASSPATH</strong>”，值为 “<strong>.;%JAVA_HOME%\lib;%JAVA_HOME%\lib\tools.jar</strong>”</li><li>编辑环境变量 “<strong>PATH</strong>”，追加两行：“<strong>%JAVA_HOME%\bin</strong>” 和 “<strong>%JAVA_HOME%\jre\bin</strong>”</li><li>测试配置：cmd 运行命令：“<strong>java -version</strong>” <strong>和 &quot;javac -version</strong>&quot;，正常输出则配置成功</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>Linux安装<ul><li>CentOS7安装：</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="0x01-docker容器编排"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x01-docker容器编排"></a> 0x01 Docker容器编排</h2><p>在漏洞环境搭建过程中，经常需要使用虚拟化环境进行漏洞环境的搭建及验证。</p><h3 id="0x0100-docker-基本原理及操作"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0100-docker-基本原理及操作"></a> 0x0100 Docker 基本原理及操作</h3><p><strong>1. Docker简介</strong></p><p>Docker 是一个开源项目，诞生于2013年年初，最初是dotCloud公司内部的一个业余项目，基于Google公司推出的Go语言实现。</p><p><strong>2. Docker的下载与安装</strong></p><blockquote><p>百度、Google、Docker官网</p></blockquote><ul><li>菜鸟教程：<a href="https://www.runoob.com/docker/docker-tutorial.html">https://www.runoob.com/docker/docker-tutorial.html</a></li></ul><p><strong>3. Docker的基本使用方法</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 使用docker前确保已经启用docker服务</span><br>systemctl stats docker # 查看<br>systemctl start docker# 启动<br>systemctl enable docker# 开启启动<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 搜索镜像</span><br>docker search tomcat# tomcat 为需要搜索的镜像的关键字<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 拉取镜像</span><br>docker pull tomcat# tomcat 为需要拉取的镜像名称，不带版本标签则默认为latest<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 查看镜像</span><br>docker images<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 删除镜像</span><br>docker rmi &lt;镜像名/镜像ID&gt;# 通过 “docker images” 查看需要删除的镜像<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 生成、运行容器</span><br>docker run &lt;opt&gt; &lt;镜像名/镜像ID&gt;<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 查看容器</span><br>docker ps -a<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 停止容器</span><br>docker stop &lt;container id&gt;# “容器ID” 通过 “docker ps -a&quot; 查看<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 启动容器</span><br>docker start &lt;container id&gt;<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 进入容器</span><br>docker exec -it &lt;container id&gt; /bin/bash<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 删除容器</span><br>docker rm &lt;container id&gt;<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 复制文件进出容器</span><br>docker cp ./flag.txt 28:/var/# 将物理机的flag.txt文件复制到编号缩写为28的容器中var目录下<br>docker cp 28:/var/flag2.txt /root/home # 同理，将容器中 /var/目录下的flag2.txt复制到物理机<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="0x0101-使用vulhub快速搭建漏洞验证环境"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0101-使用vulhub快速搭建漏洞验证环境"></a> 0x0101 使用Vulhub快速搭建漏洞验证环境</h3><p><strong>1. Vulhub简介</strong></p><p>Vulhub是一个基于<code>docker</code>和<code>docker-compose</code>的漏洞环境集合，进入对应目录并执行一条语句即可启动一个全新的漏洞环境，让漏洞复现变得更加简单，让安全研究者更加专注于漏洞原理本身。</p><p><strong>2. docker-compose简介</strong></p><p>Compose 是用于定义和运行多容器 Docker 应用程序的工具。通过 Compose，您可以使用 YML 文件来配置应用程序需要的所有服务。然后，使用一个命令，就可以从 YML 文件配置中创建并启动所有服务。</p><p>如果你还不了解 YML 文件配置，可以先阅读 <a href="https://www.runoob.com/w3cnote/yaml-intro.html">YAML 入门教程</a>。</p><p>Compose 使用的三个步骤：</p><ul><li><p>使用 Dockerfile 定义应用程序的环境。</p></li><li><p>使用 docker-compose.yml 定义构成应用程序的服务，这样它们可以在隔离环境中一起运行。</p></li><li><p>最后，执行 docker-compose up 命令来启动并运行整个应用程序。</p></li></ul><p>docker-compose.yml 的配置案例如下（配置参数参考下文）：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-comment"># yaml 配置实例</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;3&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">services:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">web:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">build:</span> <span class="hljs-string">.</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">ports:</span><br>   <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;5000:5000&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>   <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">.:/code</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">logvolume01:/var/log</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">links:</span><br>   <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">redis</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">redis:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">image:</span> <span class="hljs-string">redis</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">volumes:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">logvolume01:</span> &#123;&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3. docker-compose安装</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 运行以下命令以下载 Docker Compose 的当前稳定版本</span><br>sudo curl -L &quot;https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.24.1/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)&quot; -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 将可执行权限应用于二进制文件</span><br>sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 创建软链</span><br>sudo ln -s /usr/local/bin/docker-compose /usr/bin/docker-compose<br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 测试是否安装成功</span><br>docker-compose --version<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>4. Vulhub的下载与安装</strong></p><blockquote><p><a href="https://vulhub.org/">https://vulhub.org/</a></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Download the latest version of the vulhub (克隆下载vulhub项目)</span><br>git clone https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub.git  <br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Entry vulnerability directory (进入特定漏洞的子项目目录)</span><br>cd /path/to/vuln/ <br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Compile (optional)</span> <br>docker-compose build <br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Run (运行命令)</span><br>docker-compose up -d <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="0x02-远程调试"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x02-远程调试"></a> 0x02 远程调试</h2><p>IntelliJ IDEA 可以在无源代码的情况下进行远程调试，只需将程序的class文件或jar包添加进项目依赖即可对一些为开源的Java程序或大型中间件进行远程调试。</p><p>调试示例：</p><ul><li>“冰蝎”动态二进制加密网站管理客户端：<a href="https://github.com/rebeyond/Behinder">https://github.com/rebeyond/Behinder</a></li><li>CVE-2017-10271：对 <strong>Weblogic</strong> 进行远程调试</li><li>CVE-2017-12615：对 <strong>Tomcat</strong> 进行远程调试</li></ul><h3 id="0x0200-对-jar-包进行远程调试"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0200-对-jar-包进行远程调试"></a> 0x0200 对 jar 包进行远程调试</h3><h4 id="1-创建项目"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-创建项目"></a> 1. 创建项目：</h4><ul><li>使用 IntelliJ IDEA 创建一个Java项目，并创建 lib 文件夹将 jar 包放入。</li><li>选择 lib 文件夹，右键选择 “Add as Library…” 将 lib 文件夹添加进项目依赖。</li><li>成功添加后可以看到 jar 包中反编译后的源码。</li></ul><p><img src="images/image-20210725091917092.png" alt="image-20210725091917092"></p><h4 id="2-配置项目"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2-配置项目"></a> 2. 配置项目：</h4><ul><li>Java JVM远程调试命令行参数：</li><li><code>-agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=5005</code></li><li><code>suspend</code> 表示是否暂停程序等待调试器的连接，“y” 表示暂停，&quot;n&quot;表示不暂停。</li><li>建议选择暂停，避免程序执行过快导致一些断点无法拦截程序。</li></ul><p><img src="images/image-20210725092838833.png" alt="image-20210725092838833"></p><h4 id="3-测试配置"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#3-测试配置"></a> 3. 测试配置</h4><p>a. 命令行执行<code>Behinder.jar</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shel">java -jar -agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=y,address=5005 Behinder.jar<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="images/image-20210725094253640.png" alt="image-20210725094253640"></p><p>b. 单击 IntelliJ IDEA 右上角的 Debug 按钮，即可发现程序在断点处暂停，然后就可以进行逐步的调试了，如图：</p><p><img src="images/image-20210725094333487.png" alt="image-20210725094333487"></p><h3 id="0x0201-对-weblogic-进行远程调试"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0201-对-weblogic-进行远程调试"></a> 0x0201 对 Weblogic 进行远程调试</h3><h3 id="0x0202-对-tomcat-进行远程调试"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0202-对-tomcat-进行远程调试"></a> 0x0202 对 Tomcat 进行远程调试</h3><h3 id="0x0203-vmware虚拟机搭建远程调试环境"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x0203-vmware虚拟机搭建远程调试环境"></a> 0x0203 VMware虚拟机搭建远程调试环境</h3><h4 id="1-配置服务端"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-配置服务端"></a> 1. 配置服务端</h4><ul><li>修改 <code>docker-compose.yml</code> 文件，打开 <code>8453</code> 端口</li><li>修改 weblogic 配置文件 <code>setDomainEnv.sh</code>, 添加如下两行代码：<ul><li><code>ebugFlag=&quot;true&quot;</code></li><li><code>export debugFlag</code></li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="2-复制调试文件到物理机"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2-复制调试文件到物理机"></a> 2. 复制调试文件到物理机</h4><h2 id="0x03-项目构建工具"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#0x03-项目构建工具"></a> 0x03 项目构建工具</h2>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
